_sText:
[CS:GO Version](http://gamebanana.com/csgo/maps/170723 "CS:GO Version")
Backstory:
Terrorists have been producing illegal substances in an abandoned warehouse, isolated deep in the countryside. Satellite images have shown a rise in activity in and around the warehouse, and a police unit were set to investigate. They reported that the personnel in the warehouse were heavily armed, producing illegal substances and transporting them to other locations using the old railroad.

As a Terrorist, your objective is to:
=====================================
Eliminate the attacking CTs and defend the contraband so it can be transported.

As a Counter-Terrorist, your objective is to:
============================================
Infiltrate the warehouse and eliminate the Terrorists defending the contraband so that it can be seized.

Thank you for downloading!
